page.title: 10SUPERNATURAL EVENTS BY G&A
page.content: The following supernatural events have been reported. The Old Cottage (A Tudor Cottage) A figure of an old lady in Victorian clothing was seen standing at the bottom of the stairs.The figure said and did nothing and quickly disappeared. Rock Cottage (A Victorian Building) One night the occupier came downstairs and saw a burly man stooping over a tool box. Once when the lady's sister was in the kitchen she saw a man walking up the path,She went to answer the door and there was nobody there. One of the sisters was coming down Rock Pitch to her house.She saw someone open the gate and started walking down the hill.The sister followed the person but it disappeared round a corner
